{"id":56020,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/04/如何发送google-reader中的文章到新浪微博/","date":"2010-04-02T01:20:06Z","modified":"2010-04-02T01:20:06Z","title":"如何发送Google reader中的文章到新浪微博","content":"<p>Google Reader现在有发送到功能，目前支持的有Facebook、Twitter、Friendfeed等网站，但对于我们这些墙内的人来说还是新浪微博比较实用</p>\n<p>下面介绍如何创建一个自定义链接把文章分享到新浪微博：</p>\n<p>进入Google Reader的设置页面，进入“发送到”这个标签</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"http://jckkim.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/2010-02-17_124932.png\"><br />\n<img title=\"2010-02-17_124932\" src=\"http://jckkim.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/2010-02-17_124932.png\" alt=\"Google Reader设置\" width=\"404\" height=\"51\"><br />\n</a></p>\n<p>然后选择“创建自定义链接”：</p>\n<p><span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"http://jckkim.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/2010-02-17_125237.png\"><img title=\"2010-02-17_125237\" src=\"http://jckkim.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/2010-02-17_125237.png\" alt=\"创建自定义链接\" width=\"497\" height=\"197\"></a></p>\n<p>根据Google Reader的提示，</p>\n<p>我们在网址栏填入：<a href=\"http://v.t.sina.com.cn/share/share.php?title=$%7Btitle%7D&amp;url=$%7Burl%7D&amp;source=$%7Bsource%7D\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000\">http://v.t.sina.com.cn/share/share.php?title=${title}&amp;url=${url}&amp;source=${source}</span></a></p>\n<p>然后在网址图标中填入：<a href=\"http://t.sina.com.cn/favicon.ico\"><span style=\"color:#ff0000\">http://t.sina.com.cn/favicon.ico</span></a></p>\n<p>这样我们在Google Reader界面就能看到发送到的链接啦：</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"http://jckkim.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/2010-02-17_125819.png\"><img title=\"2010-02-17_125819\" src=\"http://jckkim.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/2010-02-17_125819.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"548\" height=\"118\"></a></p>\n","author":141,"categories":[20534],"tags":[5644,5908,8858,8339,8859]}